      </prereq>
    </thing>
  <thing id="sSorDrider" name="Dridershape" description="Your lower extremities transform, sprouting arachnid legs, as a large, pulsing thorax swells from your back.\nYou take on the form and abilities of a drider (MM 89).\nYou gain 20 temporary hit points, which disappear at the end of the spell&apos;s duration.\nYou don&apos;t gain the drider&apos;s spellcasting ability, but you retain your own.\n(Spellcasting is subject to the drider&apos;s ability scores; for instance, you can&apos;t cast wizard spells above 5th level, since your new Intelligence is only 15).\nAny held objects remain held in the new form (other gear melds into the new form as normal).\nSee page 59 for details of the polymorph subschool.\n{b}Special:{/b} This spell requires you be a Drow, or have Lloth as your patron diety.{/i}\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i}, 3.5 Edition" compset="Spell" summary="Transform into a Drider">
