  <thing id="sWizSpFrmG" name="Spider Form, Greater" description="{i}Your body inflates grotesquely as eight enormous spider legs burst through your flesh.\nAs the transformation finishes, your skin hardens into a dark exoskeleton.{/i}\n\nAs {i}lesser spider form{/i}, except you take on the form and abilities of a Huge fiendish monstrous spider (MM 289).\nYou are treated as having the spider&apos;s Hit Dice (8) for the purpose of adjudicating the special abilities gained from the fiendish template.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i}, 3.5 Edition" compset="Spell">
