  <thing id="ipDark" name="Dark" description="{b}Price:{/b} +8,000 gp\n{b}Property:{/b} Armor\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 8th\n{b}Aura: Moderate;{/b} (DC 19) illusion\n{b}Activation:{/b} &#151;\n\n{i}This armor has a dull appearance. It does not reflect light, and it maintains its color regardless of lighting conditions.{/i}\n\nDark armor is specially crafted to blend in with its surroundings when viewed with darkvision.  You gain a +5 circumstance bonus on Hide checks made to conceal yourself from creatures with darkvision. In addition (when fighting such creatures), you gain concealment.\nYou lose these benefi ts whenever you are in an area of bright light.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}invisibility{/i}.\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 4,000 gp, 320 XP, 8 days.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="ItemPower" summary="+5 Hide and concealment vs creatures with darkvision.">
