  <thing id="ipFearsom" name="Fearsom" description="{b}Price:{/b} +5,000\n{b}Property:{/b} Armor\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 3rd\n{b}Aura:{/b} Faint; (DC 16) necromancy\n{b}Activation:{/b} &#151;\n\n{i}This foul armor has a sinister appearance.\nIt is dark, almost black, and covered with sharp barbs and spikes.{/i}\n\nFearsome armor functions as if it has armor spikes (PH 124) if the armor doesn&#146;t have this feature already. In addition, when wearing this armor, you gain a +5 enhancement bonus on Intimidate checks, and you can demoralize opponents (PH 76) as a move action instead of a standard action.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Craft Magic Arms and Armor.\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 2,500 gp, 200 XP, 5 days.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="ItemPower" summary="+5 Enh on Intimidate, can demoralize as a move action.  Armor spikes.">
