    </thing>
  <thing id="ipSpdrBoon" name="Spider boon" description="{b}Price:{/b} +9,000 gp\n{b}Property:{/b} Armor\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 8th\n{b}Aura:{/b} Moderate; (DC 20) transmutation\n{b}Activation:{/b} Swift (command)\n\n{i}This armor is etched with spiderweb patterns. It is slightly slippery to the touch.{/i}\n\nSpider boon armor allows you to navigate through the sticky strands of webbing. You gain a +4 enhancement bonus on Climb and Escape Artist checks. Also, the webs of monstrous spiders or spiderkin (such as ettercaps) cannot affect you.\nThree times per day, you can increase the enhancement bonus on Climb checks to +8 and gain a climb speed equal to your base land speed. When under this effect, you can take 10 on Climb checks even if rushed or threatened. This function lasts for 8 rounds.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}freedom of movement{/i}, {i}spider climb{/i}, drow.\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 4,500 gp, 360 XP, 9 days.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="ItemPower" summary="+4 Enh to Climb and Esc Artist.  Webs dont entangle.  Plus, 3/day activation.">
