  <thing id="ioAsnCloak" name="Assassin&apos;s Cloak" description="{b}Price:{/b} 10,000 gp (12th)\n{b}Property:{/b} Shoulders\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 9th\n{b}Aura:{/b} Moderate; (DC 19) abjuration\n{b}Activation:{/b} Swift (command)\n{b}Weight:{/b} 1 lb.\n\n{i}This long gray cloak has a black lining.{/i}\n\nThree times per day, whenever you speak the command word, the {i}assassin&#146;s cloak{/i} diminishes your presence, making you seem insignificant and unimportant.\nYou gain a +10 competence bonus on Hide checks, and creatures must succeed on a DC 17 Will save to attack you. Those who succeed can attack you normally. This effect lasts 10 rounds or until you make an attack (as {i}invisibility{/i}, PH 245), whichever comes first.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Craft Wondrous Item, heightened (5th) {i}sanctuary{/i}.\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 5,000 gp, 400 XP, 10 days.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="Wondrous" summary="3/day, +10 Competance Hide and Will DC 17 to attack wearer.">
