  <thing id="ioGlooMask" name="Gloom Mask" description="{b}Price:{/b} 3,000 gp (7th)\n{b}Property:{/b} Face\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 11th\n{b}Aura:{/b} Moderate; (DC 20) evocation\n{b}Activation:{/b} Standard (command)\n{b}Weight:{/b} &#151;\n\n{i}This black mask seems to absorb the light around it. It is cool to the touch.{/i}\n\nThree times per day, you gain the ability to see in darkness out to 30 feet.  This sight penetrates all forms of darkness, even that created by a {i}deeper darkness{/i} spell; the effect lasts for 5 rounds.\nIn addition, three times per day, any spell or spell-like ability up to 3rd level with the darkness descriptor that you cast functions as if you had cast it with the {/i}Widen Spell{/i} metamagic feat.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Craft Magic Arms and Armor, {i}darkvision{/i}, {i}deeper darkness{/i}.\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 1,500 gp, 120 XP, 3 days.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="Wondrous" summary="Any spell cast with darkness discrpt Widened.  3/day darkvision 30ft.">
