  <thing id="ioMaskMatr" name="Mask of the Matriacrch" description="{b}Price:{/b} 9,000 gp (12th)\n{b}Property:{/b} Face\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 11th\n{b}Aura:{/b} Moderate; (DC 20) necromancy\n{b}Activation:{/b} Standard (command)\n{b}Weight:{/b} 5 lb.\n\n{i}This obsidian mask has been fashioned into the likeness of a drow female. Framing the face are eight straps that hold the mask in place on the wearer&#146;s head.{/i}\n\nThree times per day, you can make a gaze attack (DMG 294) against all creatures that can clearly see you and are within 30 feet.  Those who fail a DC 20 Will save cower in fear for 1 round and \nare shaken on the following round. Your gaze remains effective for 1 round.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Craft Wondrous Item, {i}imperious glare{/i} (SC).\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 4,500 gp, 360 XP, 9 days.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="Wondrous" summary="3/day, gaze attack DC 20 Will or cower for 1 rnd and shaken 2nd rnd.">
