  <thing id="ioMothCors" name="Mother&apos;s Corset" description="{b}Price:{/b} 7,200 gp (11th)\n{b}Property:{/b} Waist\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 9th\n{b}Aura:{/b} Moderate; (DC 19) transmutation\n{b}Activation:{/b} Swift (command)\n{b]Weight:{/b} 1 lb.\n\n{I}Woven into this black corset is purple thread suggestive of webbing.{/i}\n\nUp to 20 minutes each day (which you can split up as you choose), you can cause the {i}mother&#146;s corset{/i} to sprout eight spider legs from your body. You gain a climb speed of 30 feet and a +8 bonus on Climb checks. While under this effect, you can take 10 on Climb checks, even if rushed or threatened.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Craft Wondrous Item, {i}spider form{/i} (see page 63), drow.\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 3,600 gp, 288 XP, 8 days.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="Wondrous" summary="20min/day, sprout 8 spdr legs climb 30ft, +8 climb check. 10 when rushed.">
