  <thing id="ioShdwCloa" name="Shadow Cloak" description="{b}Price:{/b} 5,500 gp (10th)\n{b}Property:{/b} Shoulders\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 12th\n{b}Aura:{/b} Strong; (DC 21) conjuration, illusion\n{b}Activation:{/b} &#151; and immediate (command)\n{b}Weight:{/b} 1 lb.\n\n{i}This black cloak writhes as if it were alive.{/i}\n\nA {i}shadow cloak{/i} grants a +1 deflection bonus to AC.\nIf you are attacked, you can use the cloak three times per day to produce one or the other of the following effects:\nGain concealment for 1 round, or you can teleport to a space you can see clearly up to 10 feet in any direction.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Craft Wondrous Item, {i}blur{/i}, {i}dimension hop{/i}(PH2), {i}mage armor{/i}.\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 2,750 gp, 220 XP, 6 days.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="Wondrous" summary="+1 deflection AC, Choice of two abilities when attacked.">
