  <thing id="ioSkulEyes" name="Skullcap of Eyes" description="{b}Price:{/b} 5,500 gp (10th)\n{b}Property:{/b} Head\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 3rd\n{b}Aura:{/b} Faint; (DC 16) divination\n{b}Activation:{/b} &#151;\n{b}Weight:{/b} &#151;\n\n{i}This iron skullcap is wrought to appear as if it were covered in eyes.{/i}\n\nAs long as you wear a {i}kullcap of eyes{/i}, you gain a +5 competence bonus on Spot checks. In addition, opponents gain no bonus on attacks when they flank you.\nIf you have Improved Uncanny Dodge, the level your opponent needs to flank you increases by 2.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Craft Wondrous Item, {i}combat readiness{/i} (see page 61).\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 2,750 gp, 220 XP, 6 days.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="Wondrous" summary="+5 Spot checks, opponents gain no bonus for flank.">
