  <thing id="ioTrcklsBo" name="Trackless Boots" description="{b}Price:{/b} 1,000 gp (4th)\n{b}Property:{/b} Feet\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 3rd\n{b}Aura:{/b} Faint; (DC 16) transmutation\n{b}Activation:{/b} &#151;\n{b}Weight:{/b} &#151;\n\n{i}These boots look rather ordinary, though of fine make.{I}\n\nWhile you wear {i}trackless boots{/i}, Survival checks made to follow your trail have a &#150;5 circumstance penalty. In addition, creatures with scent cannot use this ability to detect you.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Craft Wondrous Item, {i}camouflage{/i}(SC).\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 500 gp, 40 XP, 1 day.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="Wondrous" summary="-5 penalty to follow your tracks.  Cannot be detected by {i}scent{/i} ability.">
