  <thing id="ioBraceMur" name="Bracers of Murder" description="{b}Price:{/b} 8,000 gp (11th)\n{b}Property:{/b} Arms\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 5th\n{b}Aura:{/b} Faint; (DC 17) evocation\n{b}Activation:{/b} &#151;\n{b}Weight:{/b} 3 lb.\n\n{i}Each of these burnished metal bracers is adorned with grinning skull set with onyx stones in its eye sockets.{/i}\n\n{i}Bracers of murder{/i} grant you a +2 profane bonus on attack rolls and damage rolls against flat-footed targets.\nIf you have the death attack ability, the save DC to resist your death attack increases by 2.\nIf you have sneak attack or sudden strike, reroll any result of 1 on the dice.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Craft Wondrous Item, {i}divine favor{/i}, evil.\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 4,000 gp, 200 XP, 8 days.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="Wondrous" summary="+2 prof att &amp; dmg rolls vs flatfoot targets. +2 death attack DC&apos;s. Reroll nat 1&apos;s">
