  <thing id="irDrowBloo" name="Ring of Drow Blood" description="{b}Price:{/b} 4,800 gp (9th)\n{b}Property:{/b} Ring\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 7th\n{b}Aura:{/b} Moderate; (DC 18) evocation\n{b}Activation:{/b} Standard (command)\n{b}Weight:{/b} &#151;\n\n{i}This strange silver ring appears tarnished in the light, but when viewed in the shadows, it gleams as if highly polished.{/i}\n\nA {i}ring of drow blood{/i} grants you the ability to use {i}dancing lights{/i}, {i}darkness{/i}, and {i}faerie fire{/i} as spell-like abilities, each once per day. If you already have the ability to use these spells as spell-like abilities, you gain an additional daily use for each at your normal caster level.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Forge Ring, {i}dancing lights[/i}, {i}darkness{/i}, {i}faerie fire{/i}, drow.\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 2,400 gp, 192 XP, 5 days.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="Ring" summary="1/day, (each) Gain the drow&apos;s spell-like ability.  OR 1 extra use if have.">
