  <thing id="irEscaping" name="Ring of Escaping" description="{b}Price:{/b} 3,100 gp (8th)\n{b}Property:{/b} Ring\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 7th\n{b}Aura:{/b} Moderate; (DC 18) transmutation\n{b}Activation:{/b} &#151; and swift (mental)\n{b}Weight:{/b} &#151;\n\n{i}This black metal ring is extremely smooth.\nWhen worn, it fits snugly, though you cannot feel it.{/i}\n\nA {i}ring of escaping{/i} allows you to slip away from a dangerous situation. For as long as you wear the ring, you gain a +5 competence bonus on Escape Artist checks.\nIn addition, once per day as a swift action, you gain a fly speed of 60 feet with good maneuverability for 1 round.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Forge Ring, {i}fly{/i}, {i}freedom of movement{/i}.\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 1,550 gp, 124 XP, 4 days.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="Ring" summary="+5 compet on Escape Artist.  1/day, (swift) fly 60ft (good manuver) 1 rnd.">
