  <thing id="ioBottNigh" name="Bottled Night" description="{b}Price:{/b} 200 gp (2nd)\n{b}Property:{/b} &#151; (held)\n{b}Caster Level:{/b} 3rd\n{b}Aura:{/b} Faint; (DC 16) evocation\n{b}Activation:{/b} &#151; Standard (throw)\n{b}Weight:{/b} &#151; \n\n{i}Inky black liquid swirls inside this fragile glass vial.{/i}\n\nYou can throw bottled night by making a ranged touch attack with a range increment of 10 feet. Upon impact, it instantly fills the area with magical darkness, granting concealment to all creatures in a 20-foot radius. The {i}darkness{/i} lasts for 10 rounds.\nBottled night dispels any light spell of 2nd level or lower.\n\n{i}Prerequisite:{/i} Craft Wondrous Item, {i}darkness{/i}.\n{i}Cost to Create:{/i} 100 gp, 8 XP, 1 day.\n\n{b}Source:{/b} {i}Drow of the Underdark{/i} 3.5 Edition" compset="Wondrous" summary="Thrown, fills 20ft-radius area with darkness as the spell.">
